data.description: This move-in ready home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. You will feel right at home from entry into the spacious living room that leads to the kitchen. Near the garage door you will find the down stairs half bath. As you head up stairs you will notice the three bedrooms that host 2 full baths. This home also has leased solar panels through SunPowerthat buyers will need to assume loan. Roof in less than 10 years old. AC and heat are less than 5 years old.
